WEBVTT

00:00:00.968 --> 00:00:04.968
I'm thrilled to be talking to you
by this high-tech method.

00:00:06.167 --> 00:00:08.079
Of all humans who have ever lived,

00:00:08.103 --> 00:00:12.712
the overwhelming majority
would have found what we are doing here

00:00:12.736 --> 00:00:15.196
incomprehensible, unbelievable.

00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:18.753
Because, for thousands of centuries,

00:00:18.777 --> 00:00:21.712
in the dark time
before the scientific revolution

00:00:21.736 --> 00:00:23.544
and the Enlightenment,

00:00:23.568 --> 00:00:26.536
people had low expectations.

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:29.576
For their lives,
for their descendants' lives.

